snippet.title: "Star Fox 2D: War of Lylat" fangame demo playthrough
snippet.description:
Click the closed caption button for crummy commentary!

A demo shown off at NCFC 2007 (Nintendo Community Fangame Convention), developed in Game Maker by Central Dynamo. Download it here:
http://www.mediafire.com/?uryqmz2i2kg

The training stage of Star Fox 64 reimagined as a vertically-scrolling shmup. An interesting idea, but there's not enough here to really sell it.
